{"tid":448500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港鐵出軌】回廠列車突出軌 車卡彈起撞爆石屎梯","createTime":"2017-10-26T09:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T16:11:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"caf42ff76297d4bf8d2e2190eb958344044007ec","tid":448500,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171026/large/1509002138_12dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171026%2Flarge%2F1509002138_12dc.jpg&h=31b788f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171026/large/1509003103_f69d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171026%2Flarge%2F1509003103_f69d.jpg&h=d5c144f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171026/large/1509002814_b0eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171026%2Flarge%2F1509002814_b0eb.jpg&h=02699d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【16:17】機電署稱今日已派員到車廠了解及調查出軌意外，港鐵一般需於4至6星期內就意外向運輸署及運房局等提交調查報告<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發生罕見的出軌意外！消息稱，一輛港鐵列車今日凌晨在返柴灣車廠時，其中一卡車廂突然出軌，出軌的車廂猛撞向清潔工作用的月台，並撞翻了一條供車長上落列車用的石屎樓梯，列車的車身及其中一車門被撞毀，幸意外中據悉無人受傷。意外現因眾說紛紜，有港鐵人員懷疑意外起因是列車其中一車廂車底的氣墊(Air suspension)突然爆裂，令車廂彈起及出軌，但亦有說法指意外起因疑是車廂轉向架的車輪出問題，機電署與港鐵正調查意外真正原因。<br />\n<br />\n意外發生後，港鐵未有公開事件或解釋意外，有港鐵職員稱關注意外會否與列車失修有關，因肇禍的港鐵列車據悉已使用多年。<br />\n<br />\n本身是港鐵車長的葵青區議員梁志成稱他亦聽聞過有關意外，他形容今次列車出軌屬罕見及嚴重意外。因若在平日行車時發生意外可能會令乘客受傷及令港鐵服務癱瘓；若意外涉氣墊爆列並且於維修列車期間發生，更可能危及維修人員的生命安全。故他促請港鐵徹查事件原因及加強對瀕淘汰老舊列車的安全檢查，以策安全。<br />\n<br />\n據梁所知，港鐵列車的車底氣墊系統，是用來避震以及調節車廂高低之用，因車廂若有不同的載客量（載重量），列車地板的高低會有分別。故列車的系統會利用氣墊自動調節車廂地板的高度，使之與車站月台的高度大致相同，讓乘客可安全上落列車。"},{"pid":"1c105e49d06dc73f122d5671ba5d6b5db5f76815","tid":448500,"uid":52062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"爛左 要整 無錢 加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa638a3561ff5c6f4136d514b152a2f037dfc1d","tid":448500,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"爛左 要整 無錢 加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064e5e49adfcefed7497768903f04eb469f14a11","tid":448500,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"嘩嘩嘩&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"d0ae6d69c0965e634da44acc4d9757fd7b0294d1","tid":448500,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"高層：下個月加價先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6388dccad4884aab1f80275c0e5d8ed6634ca40a","tid":448500,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:37:11.000Z","msg":"極危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923b24b9e0985960465129489dfa93ee6f7ad571","tid":448500,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:38:28.000Z","msg":"好多蘋果"},{"pid":"b4cf361fc72e2dcb3a499857f5633e49a547bb09","tid":448500,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:41:19.000Z","msg":"爛左 唔整 買支那車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa183dc8e5e6d4c6e3b991a76249645070eaeff","tid":448500,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cc02a633123c5afce005d33643d5abca954b9f","tid":448500,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:53:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8431845263d0c285a8ff2fd29ab457d9f1d5c110","tid":4485