\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ef4b5fe173b8b5933d21c147985d52b9357ad0","tid":448500,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全面淘汰英國車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌英車用到殘啦<br />\n又嘈又唔好坐<br />\n<br />\n利申支車一鳩樣垃圾"}]}